#* '''1957''', [[w:Sarvepalli_Radhakrishnan|S. Radhakrishnan]] and C. A. Moore (eds.), ''A Sourcebook in Indian Philosophy'', Princeton Univ. Press, p. 38,
#*: Until we are released from the law of ''karma'' and reach ''moksha'' or deliverance, we will be in '''''samsara''''' or the time process.

